You probably won't get the chance to read this, but i got an idea for the AMG.
Since you talked about tuning and so on for your TT, you could wrap or foil your Syndicate Logo on to a part of your car (hood or doors or windshields).
Furthermore you could find a interior aftermarket store and let them rewrap your dashboard with your Lion logo aswell. ("Neidfaktor" is the only one i know of , but it is in Germany).
Gives it a real personal touch in my opinion.

PS: High-pressure cleaner for your car at home might be a good choice aswell :D

You could get one with a soap dispenser and different brush adapters

Hope you have loads of fun with your beauty.
Greetings from Austria :D
